#: ../../source/glossary.rst:2 5be303ba7a16486a827e3529c340c42d
msgid "术语表"
msgstr "Glossary"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:4 257ee9b6872e4fa186051f10b7968a48
msgid ""
"本页整理使用 Godot-FmodPlayer 时常见的 FMOD 与音频术语。内容参考 `FMOD API Glossary "
"<https://www.fmod.com/docs/2.02/api/glossary.html>`_， 并根据 Godot 引擎、FMOD "
"Core API 与 Godot-FmodPlayer 的实际用法重新说明。"
msgstr ""
"This page collects common FMOD and audio terms used with Godot-"
"FmodPlayer. It refers to the `FMOD API Glossary "
"<https://www.fmod.com/docs/2.02/api/glossary.html>`_ and adapts the "
"explanations to Godot Engine, the FMOD Core API, and Godot-FmodPlayer "
"usage."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:10 789b32d944af4df0b33210eab252ca35
msgid ""
"本页不是 FMOD 官方文档的中文翻译，也不替代 FMOD 官方许可、API 文档或技术支持。 FMOD、FMOD Engine 等名称归 "
"Firelight Technologies Pty Ltd 所有。发布项目时请以 `FMOD Legal Information "
"<https://www.fmod.com/legal>`_ 与 `FMOD Licensing "
"<https://www.fmod.com/licensing>`_ 为准。"
msgstr ""
"This page is not an official Chinese translation of the FMOD "
"documentation and does not replace the official FMOD license, API "
"documentation, or technical support. Names such as FMOD and FMOD Engine "
"belong to Firelight Technologies Pty Ltd. When publishing a project, "
"always follow `FMOD Legal Information <https://www.fmod.com/legal>`_ and "
"the official licensing terms."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:18 5d9d11a72663480aa6944c1f0fcd2589
msgid "2D 与 3D"
msgstr "2D and 3D"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:20 8dcf46551f70484b925fe6c834e59489
msgid ""
"2D 声音不会参与空间定位。它通常适合 UI 音效、背景音乐、旁白、菜单音效等不需要跟随场景位置变化的声音。 在 Godot-FmodPlayer"
" 中，:ref:`FmodAudioStreamPlayer<FmodAudioStreamPlayer>` 默认更接近 2D 播放用法。"
msgstr ""
"2D sounds do not participate in spatial positioning. They are usually "
"suitable for UI sound effects, background music, narration, menu sounds, "
"and other sounds that do not need to follow scene positions. In Godot-"
"FmodPlayer, :ref:`FmodAudioStreamPlayer<FmodAudioStreamPlayer>` is closer"
" to the default 2D playback workflow."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:23 7de3c41588f14235ad84a1a09dbf85d1
msgid ""
"3D 声音会根据声源和监听器之间的位置关系计算音量、声像、距离衰减、遮挡和多普勒效果。 在 Godot-FmodPlayer "
"中，:ref:`FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D<FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D>` 会把 Godot "
"节点的全局位置同步到 FMOD 通道， 适合脚步、武器、环境物件、车辆、怪物叫声等来自世界空间的声音。"
msgstr ""
"3D sounds calculate volume, pan, distance attenuation, occlusion, and "
"Doppler effects from the relationship between the sound source and the "
"listener. In Godot-FmodPlayer, "
":ref:`FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D<FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D>` synchronizes the "
"Godot node global position to the FMOD channel."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:29 b2415098a6c54748a6864b91b14a263d
msgid ""
":ref:`FmodChannelControl.set_3d_level()<FmodChannelControl-set_3d_level>`"
" 可以调整 3D 混合比例。 这在需要让一个声音部分保持空间感、部分保持稳定声像时很有用。"
msgstr ""
":ref:`FmodChannelControl.set_3d_level()<FmodChannelControl-"
"set_3d_level>` adjusts the 3D blend amount. This is useful when a sound "
"should keep some spatial feeling while retaining a stable pan image."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:35 b7353364fc8048419e8ea1064b629c8f
msgid "音频资产"
msgstr "Audio Asset"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:37 7de19d7582c14d39b11b04bbd719e474
msgid ""
"音频资产是项目中可播放的声音数据。它可以是 ``wav``、``ogg``、``mp3``、``flac`` 等独立音频文件， "
"也可以是运行时已经能够读取的其他 FMOD 支持格式。"
msgstr ""
"An audio asset is playable sound data in the project. It may be an "
"independent audio file such as ``wav``, ``ogg``, ``mp3``, or ``flac``, or"
" another runtime-readable format supported by FMOD."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:40 fd5824f7d1134fa5864056b2edb61de1
msgid ""
"在 Godot-FmodPlayer 中，常见做法是把音频文件导入为 "
":ref:`FmodAudioStream<FmodAudioStream>`， 再交给 "
":ref:`FmodAudioStreamPlayer<FmodAudioStreamPlayer>`、:ref:`FmodAudioStreamPlayer2D<FmodAudioStreamPlayer2D>`"
" 或 :ref:`FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D<FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D>` 播放。"
msgstr ""
"In Godot-FmodPlayer, the common workflow is to import audio files as "
":ref:`FmodAudioStream<FmodAudioStream>` and play them through "
":ref:`FmodAudioStreamPlayer<FmodAudioStreamPlayer>`, "
":ref:`FmodAudioStreamPlayer2D<FmodAudioStreamPlayer2D>`, or "
":ref:`FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D<FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D>`."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:47 f743d28f15024019872353765b949fef
msgid "音频通道"
msgstr "Audio Channel"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:49 0959a35e57ab41f7b61a8ac8337c8b43
msgid "音频通道可以指两种不同概念，需要区分："
msgstr "Audio channel can mean two different things, so the distinction matters:"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:51 8ec5f9e74b5e448e843469b10998a560
msgid "**声道**：音频信号里的扬声器通道，例如单声道、左声道、右声道、5.1 环绕声中的多个输出通道。"
msgstr ""
"**Speaker channel**: A speaker channel in the audio signal, such as mono,"
" left, right, or multiple output channels in 5.1 surround."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:52 47c0add3f4ba4402beb018e9e9e5c720
msgid ""
"**FMOD Channel**：FMOD 中的一次声音播放实例，对应 Godot-FmodPlayer 的 "
":ref:`FmodChannel<FmodChannel>`。"
msgstr ""
"**FMOD Channel**: One sound playback instance in FMOD, corresponding to "
":ref:`FmodChannel<FmodChannel>` in Godot-FmodPlayer."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:54 e381f37d708c4d70a1d50af9b75f24e3
msgid ""
"例如，一个立体声音效文件有两个声道；当它被播放一次时，FMOD 会为这次播放创建或分配一个 Channel。 "
"同一个声音同时播放三次，就可能对应三个不同的 :ref:`FmodChannel<FmodChannel>`。"
msgstr ""
"For example, a stereo sound effect file has two speaker channels. When it"
" is played once, FMOD creates or assigns one Channel for that playback. "
"If the same sound plays three times at once, it may correspond to three "
"different :ref:`FmodChannel<FmodChannel>` objects."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:60 416a529a6dc049b8b643ae92090b493e
msgid "Bus"
msgstr "Bus"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:62 5860aefe2c4f491f9fa30cb89bf1feab
msgid ""
"Bus 即音频总线，用来把一组声音集中到同一个混音路径上。常见总线包括 ``Music``、``SFX``、``Voice`` 和 "
"``Ambient``。"
msgstr ""
"A Bus is an audio bus used to collect a group of sounds into the same "
"mixing route. Common buses include ``Music``, ``SFX``, ``Voice``, and "
"``Ambient``."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:64 d5d24220b55a456a8364829127eae504
msgid ""
"Godot-FmodPlayer 会把 Godot 的 `AudioServer`_ 总线结构同步为 "
":ref:`FmodAudioBusLayout<FmodAudioBusLayout>`， 并用 "
":ref:`FmodAudioBus<FmodAudioBus>` / "
":ref:`FmodChannelGroup<FmodChannelGroup>` 管理实际混音。 这样可以用类似 Godot "
"原生音频总线的方式控制 FMOD 声音，同时仍然使用 FMOD 的 DSP、通道组和性能数据。"
msgstr ""
"Godot-FmodPlayer synchronizes Godot's `AudioServer`_ bus structure into "
":ref:`FmodAudioBusLayout<FmodAudioBusLayout>` and uses "
":ref:`FmodAudioBus<FmodAudioBus>` / "
":ref:`FmodChannelGroup<FmodChannelGroup>` to control FMOD-side mixing."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:71 28b6423894ad47dcb18332792d9b8faa
msgid "Channel"
msgstr "Channel"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:73 ba5ca4d5487142c0992324e5df36de40
msgid ""
"Channel 是 FMOD 中一次正在播放或由虚拟语音系统托管的声音实例。它可以控制音量、暂停、音高、循环点、播放位置、 3D 属性、DSP "
"链和回调。"
msgstr ""
"A Channel is one sound instance currently playing in FMOD, or managed by "
"the virtual voice system. It can control volume, pause, pitch, loop "
"points, playback position, 3D properties, DSP chains, and callbacks."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:76 839a3fd860174e45bbb00059fa558a5b
msgid ""
"在 Godot-FmodPlayer 中，播放节点内部会维护一个 :ref:`FmodChannel<FmodChannel>`。 "
"如果需要更细的控制，可以取得当前播放通道，再调用 :ref:`FmodChannelControl<FmodChannelControl>` 或 "
":ref:`FmodChannel<FmodChannel>` 的方法。"
msgstr ""
"In Godot-FmodPlayer, playback nodes maintain a "
":ref:`FmodChannel<FmodChannel>` internally. If finer control is needed, "
"get the current playback channel and call "
":ref:`FmodChannelControl<FmodChannelControl>` or "
":ref:`FmodChannel<FmodChannel>` methods."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:83 3bc8613a19cd40a8920fa086c2a07379
msgid "ChannelGroup"
msgstr "ChannelGroup"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:85 eae497092c7e4c108e8b85adaef0e816
msgid ""
"ChannelGroup 是多个 Channel 或子 ChannelGroup 的混音容器。它适合做分组控制，例如同时降低所有音乐音量、 "
"暂停一组环境声，或给整个 ``SFX`` 总线添加一个滤波器。"
msgstr ""
"A ChannelGroup is a mixing container for multiple Channels or child "
"ChannelGroups. It is useful for grouped control, such as lowering all "
"music, pausing a group of ambience sounds, or adding a filter to the "
"whole ``SFX`` bus."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:88 beb6c74ada964cc88b1c53097d8a9ee5
msgid ""
"在 Godot-FmodPlayer 中，:ref:`FmodChannelGroup<FmodChannelGroup>` "
"通常由总线系统创建和管理。 普通项目优先通过 :doc:`user_guide/mixer` 中的总线接口操作；只有在需要底层控制时才直接访问 "
"ChannelGroup。"
msgstr ""
"In Godot-FmodPlayer, :ref:`FmodChannelGroup<FmodChannelGroup>` is usually"
" created and managed by the bus system. For regular projects, prefer the "
"bus APIs described in :doc:`user_guide/mixer`; access ChannelGroup "
"directly only when lower-level control is needed."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:94 640aef804f8143179b4d9f709481ab3e
msgid "ChannelControl"
msgstr "ChannelControl"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:96 0270ad4799d44685bfb56e00cc99d28e
msgid ""
"ChannelControl 是 Channel 和 ChannelGroup 共享的一组控制能力。它包含音量、静音、暂停、音高、3D "
"属性、声像矩阵、 DSP 插入、淡变点和回调等接口。"
msgstr ""
"ChannelControl is the shared control surface of Channel and ChannelGroup."
" It includes APIs for volume, mute, pause, pitch, 3D properties, pan "
"matrix, DSP insertion, fade points, and callbacks."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:99 8722426d24974b19adeb1730be15bf15
msgid ""
"Godot-FmodPlayer 中的 :ref:`FmodChannel<FmodChannel>` 与 "
":ref:`FmodChannelGroup<FmodChannelGroup>` 都继承自 "
":ref:`FmodChannelControl<FmodChannelControl>`。因此，很多播放控制方法既能用于单个声音，也能用于一整组声音。"
msgstr ""
"Both :ref:`FmodChannel<FmodChannel>` and "
":ref:`FmodChannelGroup<FmodChannelGroup>` in Godot-FmodPlayer inherit "
"from :ref:`FmodChannelControl<FmodChannelControl>`, so many playback and "
"mixing controls are shared."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:105 3b4f4c7fce07411db4f61e68d208e17f
msgid "DSP"
msgstr "DSP"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:107 fb28cc435c5440a68049d81ba373e3d2
msgid ""
"DSP 是 Digital Signal Processing 的缩写，表示数字信号处理单元。混响、均衡器、滤波器、延迟、失真、压缩器、 "
"频谱分析器等都可以作为 DSP 参与音频处理。"
msgstr ""
"DSP stands for Digital Signal Processing. Reverb, equalizers, filters, "
"delay, distortion, compressors, and spectrum analyzers can all "
"participate in audio processing as DSP units."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:110 d464d563aa9d47068f49fa78a3cc3629
msgid ""
"在 Godot-FmodPlayer 中，:ref:`FmodDSP<FmodDSP>` 可以添加到某个 Channel、ChannelGroup"
" 或总线相关的混音路径上。 如果多个声音需要同一种效果，通常把 DSP 放在对应总线上更容易维护，也比给每个声音单独创建效果更省资源。"
msgstr ""
"In Godot-FmodPlayer, :ref:`FmodDSP<FmodDSP>` can be added to a Channel, "
"ChannelGroup, or bus-related mixing route. If multiple sounds need the "
"same effect, placing the DSP on the corresponding bus is usually easier "
"to maintain and cheaper than creating the effect for every sound."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:116 85b129cba7f945c9b96758f82f60f171
msgid "DSP 链"
msgstr "DSP Chain"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:118 5538af25e12f49ab990a8514b7cdda56
msgid ""
"DSP 链是多个 DSP 按顺序连接形成的处理路径。声音进入链后，会依次经过这些处理单元。 "
"不同顺序会产生不同结果，例如先失真再混响，和先混响再失真，听感通常不同。"
msgstr ""
"A DSP chain is a processing path formed by connecting multiple DSPs in "
"order. Once sound enters the chain, it passes through each processing "
"unit sequentially. Different orders produce different results; distortion"
" before reverb usually sounds different from reverb before distortion."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:123 6383e8a27ff44dceb55f27b8c8206915
msgid ""
"在 Godot-FmodPlayer 中，可以通过 :ref:`FmodChannelControl.add_dsp"
"()<FmodChannelControl-add_dsp>`、 :ref:`FmodChannelControl.remove_dsp"
"()<FmodChannelControl-remove_dsp>` 和 "
":ref:`FmodChannelControl.set_dsp_index()<FmodChannelControl-"
"set_dsp_index>` 调整 DSP 链。"
msgstr ""
"In Godot-FmodPlayer, you can control the chain with "
":ref:`FmodChannelControl.add_dsp()<FmodChannelControl-add_dsp>`, "
":ref:`FmodChannelControl.remove_dsp()<FmodChannelControl-remove_dsp>`, "
"and :ref:`FmodChannelControl.set_dsp_index()<FmodChannelControl-"
"set_dsp_index>`."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:130 7a99d8a11a644bc2948eefc2c500b1a6
msgid "DSP Clock"
msgstr "DSP Clock"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:132 63c317bc9675478cae90abc6c0e4a7f4
msgid "DSP Clock 是 FMOD 混音器使用的样本级时间计数。它常用于精确调度播放、延迟启动、淡入淡出或和其他声音对齐。"
msgstr ""
"DSP Clock is FMOD mixer time counted at sample precision. It is commonly "
"used for precise playback scheduling, delayed starts, fades, or aligning "
"sounds."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:134 6d552fae320043c1aea962b99af65b45
msgid ""
"在 Godot-FmodPlayer 中，:ref:`FmodChannelControl.get_dsp_clock"
"()<FmodChannelControl-get_dsp_clock>`、 :ref:`FmodChannelControl.set_delay"
"()<FmodChannelControl-set_delay>` 和淡变点接口可以用于需要样本级同步的场景。 "
"普通按钮音效和环境声通常不需要直接处理 DSP Clock。"
msgstr ""
"In Godot-FmodPlayer, APIs such as :ref:`FmodChannelControl.get_dsp_clock"
"()<FmodChannelControl-get_dsp_clock>` and "
":ref:`FmodChannelControl.set_delay()<FmodChannelControl-set_delay>` "
"expose related timing controls."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:141 c1cd133569104ea583503c889ddfe73d
msgid "Listener"
msgstr "Listener"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:143 ac0e1de70b2a4ff6b129ac2959f27f7d
msgid "Listener 即监听器，表示玩家“听见世界”的位置和朝向。3D 声音会根据监听器与声源之间的距离、方向和相对速度计算结果。"
msgstr ""
"A Listener represents where the player hears the world from, including "
"position and orientation. 3D sounds are calculated from the distance, "
"direction, and relative velocity between the listener and the source."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:145 7aadd514f8b6416289271ee69d435a4b
msgid ""
"在 Godot 场景中，监听器通常跟随玩家、主摄像机或当前激活的 ``AudioListener3D``。 使用 "
":ref:`FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D<FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D>` 时，需要确保 FMOD "
"系统能获得正确的监听器变换， 否则 3D 声音可能听起来位置不对或距离衰减异常。"
msgstr ""
"In a Godot scene, the listener usually follows the player, main camera, "
"or active ``AudioListener3D``. When using "
":ref:`FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D<FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D>`, make sure the "
"FMOD system receives the correct listener transform; otherwise 3D sound "
"direction or distance may be wrong."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:152 ac46a3b908204f1abfe7c85c5fc667e9
msgid "Sound"
msgstr "Sound"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:154 220b6977def5430e8372ee38839ac3cb
msgid "Sound 是 FMOD 对音频数据的运行时表示。它通常由文件、内存数据或流式数据创建，然后通过 System 播放为 Channel。"
msgstr ""
"Sound is FMOD's runtime representation of audio data. It is usually "
"created from a file, memory data, or streaming data, and then played by "
"the System as a Channel."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:156 207a9e422dca447f9470949e39730cc9
msgid ""
"在 Godot-FmodPlayer 中，:ref:`FmodAudioStream<FmodAudioStream>` 会在需要时创建底层 "
":ref:`FmodSound<FmodSound>`。 这让资源可以先作为 Godot 资源存在，真正播放或查询底层对象时再交给 FMOD "
"创建声音。"
msgstr ""
"In Godot-FmodPlayer, :ref:`FmodAudioStream<FmodAudioStream>` creates the "
"underlying :ref:`FmodSound<FmodSound>` only when needed. This lets the "
"resource exist as a Godot resource first, and only hand the sound to FMOD"
" when playback or low-level access is required."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:162 436646e2fcc04382975e8d8d88e5f1c9
msgid "Stream 与 Sample"
msgstr "Stream and Sample"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:164 5ea00a05f44f41a2a91ac4a88b2ba7a2
msgid ""
"Stream 表示边读取边解码的播放方式，适合音乐、长旁白、长环境声等体积较大的音频。 Sample "
"表示把音频数据加载到内存后播放，适合短音效、频繁触发的 UI 声和需要低延迟响应的声音。"
msgstr ""
"Stream means audio is read and decoded while playing, which is suitable "
"for large audio such as music, long narration, and long ambience. Sample "
"means the audio data is loaded into memory before playback, which is "
"suitable for short sound effects, frequently triggered UI sounds, and "
"low-latency responses."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:167 44e72be8ea284da39e4909211f94d620
msgid ""
"在 Godot-FmodPlayer 中，可以通过 :ref:`FmodAudioStream<FmodAudioStream>` "
"的创建模式选择更适合的加载方式。 一般来说，长音频优先使用流式播放，短音效优先使用样本加载。"
msgstr ""
"In Godot-FmodPlayer, you choose the more suitable loading method through "
"the creation mode of :ref:`FmodAudioStream<FmodAudioStream>`. In general,"
" prefer streaming for long audio and sample loading for short sound "
"effects."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:173 d09eb9d96da0483d888ecde8d25ccdfb
msgid "Virtual Channel"
msgstr "Virtual Channel"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:175 bf396a65ddf8469f988fbf80b01a8dbf
msgid ""
"Virtual Channel 即虚拟通道。当同时播放的声音很多时，FMOD 可以让听不见或优先级较低的声音进入虚拟状态。 "
"虚拟通道仍然保留播放时间和状态，但不一定消耗完整的混音资源。"
msgstr ""
"A Virtual Channel is a channel in FMOD's virtual voice system. When many "
"sounds play at the same time, FMOD may virtualize inaudible or low-"
"priority sounds. A virtual channel keeps playback time and state, but may"
" not consume full mixing resources."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:178 bdceccb9f8a5427ab0a0c7387bb64868
msgid ""
"在 Godot-FmodPlayer 中，可以通过 :ref:`FmodChannel.is_virtual()<FmodChannel-"
"is_virtual>` 查询某个通道是否处于虚拟状态。 这对调试大量环境声、粒子音效或开放世界场景中的声音预算很有帮助。"
msgstr ""
"In Godot-FmodPlayer, :ref:`FmodChannel.is_virtual()<FmodChannel-"
"is_virtual>` can query whether a channel is virtual. This is useful when "
"debugging large ambience sets, particle sounds, or sound budgets in open-"
"world scenes."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:184 dc75ea5e9a764421854d32dce95085a2
msgid "Rolloff"
msgstr "Rolloff"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:186 6c6730a419d74e2e9e57f960fcd7bf6e
msgid "Rolloff 表示 3D 声音随距离变远而衰减的曲线。不同曲线会影响声音从近处到远处的听感变化。"
msgstr ""
"Rolloff is the curve describing how a 3D sound attenuates as distance "
"increases. Different curves change how the sound feels from near to far."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:188 64d4b489194641e9a4201c8a537e59c4
msgid ""
"在 Godot-FmodPlayer 中，3D 播放节点和 "
":ref:`FmodChannelControl<FmodChannelControl>` 提供最小距离、最大距离、 "
"自定义衰减曲线等设置。制作空间音频时，建议先调好 ``min_distance`` 和 ``max_distance``， "
"再根据项目需要调整更复杂的衰减行为。"
msgstr ""
"In Godot-FmodPlayer, 3D playback nodes and "
":ref:`FmodChannelControl<FmodChannelControl>` provide settings such as "
"minimum distance, maximum distance, and custom attenuation curves. For "
"spatial audio, start by tuning ``min_distance`` and ``max_distance``."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:195 8d80f3f15d5d4ed2ab7a0f79c8697f7c
msgid "Doppler"
msgstr "Doppler"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:197 56f2edaf2b71407883132de2904fef12
msgid "Doppler 即多普勒效果。当声源和监听器之间存在相对速度时，音高会发生变化。 快速掠过的车辆、飞行物或高速移动的物体可以使用该效果增强速度感。"
msgstr ""
"Doppler is the pitch shift caused by relative velocity between a sound "
"source and the listener. Fast passing vehicles, projectiles, or moving "
"objects can use it to enhance the sense of speed."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:200 517f3f8e0aa643cbb70c7ba5ab16aa82
msgid ""
"在 Godot-FmodPlayer "
"中，:ref:`FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D<FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D>` 会同步位置和速度相关信息。 "
"如果效果过强或不符合游戏风格，可以通过多普勒相关设置降低影响。"
msgstr ""
"In Godot-FmodPlayer, "
":ref:`FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D<FmodAudioStreamPlayer3D>` synchronizes "
"position and velocity information. If the effect is too strong or does "
"not fit the game style, reduce the Doppler-related settings."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:206 8c263b0b323f46af8b73a9c616571469
msgid "Occlusion"
msgstr "Occlusion"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:208 d5b59e7c877a4a2092e9ecdf21a478ba
msgid "Occlusion 即遮挡。它描述墙体、地形或其他几何体阻挡声音传播后，音量和高频内容被削弱的效果。"
msgstr ""
"Occlusion describes how walls, terrain, or other geometry block sound "
"propagation, reducing volume and high-frequency content."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:210 9161ad1138f0455f8dcbed7233503b2b
msgid ""
"Godot-FmodPlayer 提供 "
":ref:`FmodGeometryInstance3D<FmodGeometryInstance3D>`，可以把场景几何体注册到 FMOD "
"Geometry 系统。 适合需要门后声音、墙后声音、房间隔音等空间表现的项目。"
msgstr ""
"Godot-FmodPlayer provides "
":ref:`FmodGeometryInstance3D<FmodGeometryInstance3D>` to register scene "
"geometry with FMOD Geometry. It is suitable for projects that need sounds"
" behind doors, sounds behind walls, or room isolation effects."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:216 08ab57d9c7fd4b8fa713e289f0c3bc69
msgid "Pan 与 Mix Matrix"
msgstr "Pan and Mix Matrix"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:218 729736e0e67f40e6b91e0bdbc27a66b2
msgid ""
"Pan 即声像，通常用于控制声音在左右声道或环绕声场中的位置。Mix Matrix 则是更底层的输入到输出声道矩阵， "
"可以精确控制每个输入声道如何分配到输出声道。"
msgstr ""
"Pan usually controls where a sound sits in the left/right channels or "
"surround field. Mix Matrix is a lower-level input-to-output channel "
"matrix that can precisely control how each input channel is distributed "
"to output channels."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:221 99717232761044c5bc7a4ab964c08f63
msgid ""
"在 Godot-FmodPlayer 中，简单左右声像可以使用 :ref:`FmodChannelControl.set_pan"
"()<FmodChannelControl-set_pan>`。 如果需要多声道或特殊路由，可以使用 "
":ref:`FmodChannelControl.set_mix_matrix()<FmodChannelControl-"
"set_mix_matrix>`。"
msgstr ""
"In Godot-FmodPlayer, simple left/right panning can use "
":ref:`FmodChannelControl.set_pan()<FmodChannelControl-set_pan>`. For "
"multi-channel or special routing, use "
":ref:`FmodChannelControl.set_mix_matrix()<FmodChannelControl-"
"set_mix_matrix>`."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:227 f380b08ef30f445b81034fdb688b5b7b
msgid "Mix Matrix"
msgstr "Mix Matrix"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:229 46fb213eddff4905beecd0e0b6a0dffa
msgid ""
"Mix Matrix 即混音矩阵，用来控制 **输入声道** 如何分配到 **输出声道**。 "
"可以把它理解成一张权重表：每一列是一个输入声道，每一行是一个输出声道，表格中的数值表示 “这个输入声道有多少信号送到这个输出声道”。"
msgstr ""
"Mix Matrix controls how **input channels** are distributed to **output "
"channels**. You can think of it as a weight table: each column is an "
"input channel, each row is an output channel, and each value says how "
"much of that input channel is sent to that output channel."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:233 17795e5f271548bd80d171bd88f3bfca
msgid "以一个立体声输入原样送到立体声输出为例："
msgstr "For example, a stereo input sent unchanged to stereo output:"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:235 c6362d7ad1ff4e25a4e8e3725ea7c99d
msgid "立体声输入原样输出到立体声输出的混音矩阵"
msgstr "Mix matrix for sending stereo input unchanged to stereo output"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:240 421cc51423844f93bed5e0b86d7f49e9
msgid "这个矩阵表示左声道只进左扬声器，右声道只进右扬声器。用更直观的形式写就是："
msgstr ""
"This matrix means the left channel goes only to the left speaker, and the"
" right channel goes only to the right speaker. Written more directly:"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:242 ceda5092b2ce437a9676e64e8b984828
msgid ""
"输出 L = 输入 L * 1.0 + 输入 R * 0.0\n"
"输出 R = 输入 L * 0.0 + 输入 R * 1.0"
msgstr ""
"Output L = Input L * 1.0 + Input R * 0.0\n"
"Output R = Input L * 0.0 + Input R * 1.0"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:247 cfd628e895a145b28e8f802e11c5cc09
msgid ""
"在 Godot-FmodPlayer 中，:ref:`FmodChannelControl.set_mix_matrix"
"()<FmodChannelControl-set_mix_matrix>` 接收一个 "
"``PackedFloat32Array``，并指定输出声道数、输入声道数和输入声道步长。 矩阵按“输出行优先”的方式书写：先写输出 0 "
"接收各输入的权重，再写输出 1，以此类推。"
msgstr ""
"In Godot-FmodPlayer, :ref:`FmodChannelControl.set_mix_matrix"
"()<FmodChannelControl-set_mix_matrix>` accepts a ``PackedFloat32Array`` "
"and specifies the output channel count, input channel count, and input "
"channel stride."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:251 fc4d6120a57944f783e7ff661bf70bac
msgid "下面示例把立体声左右声道对调："
msgstr "The example below swaps the left and right channels of a stereo sound:"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:253 a51ac308fad646b7842834f2f44dc231
msgid ""
"func swap_stereo(channel: FmodChannel) -> void:\n"
"    var matrix := PackedFloat32Array([\n"
"        0.0, 1.0, # Out L = In R\n"
"        1.0, 0.0, # Out R = In L\n"
"    ])\n"
"\n"
"    channel.set_mix_matrix(matrix, 2, 2)"
msgstr ""
"func swap_stereo(channel: FmodChannel) -> void:\n"
"    var matrix := PackedFloat32Array([\n"
"        0.0, 1.0, # Out L = In R\n"
"        1.0, 0.0, # Out R = In L\n"
"    ])\n"
"\n"
"    channel.set_mix_matrix(matrix, 2, 2)"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:263 5472a591b73a4ef3bd4266b8b7e0d6bc
msgid ""
"如果只是想调整单个播放实例的左右位置，优先使用 :ref:`FmodChannelControl.set_pan"
"()<FmodChannelControl-set_pan>`。 Mix Matrix "
"更适合处理多声道格式转换、特殊声道路由、左右声道互换、单声道偏置和调试音频资产等场景。"
msgstr ""
"If you only want to adjust the left/right position of one playback "
"instance, prefer :ref:`FmodChannelControl.set_pan()<FmodChannelControl-"
"set_pan>`. Mix Matrix is better for multi-channel format conversion, "
"special channel routing, left/right swapping, mono biasing, and debugging"
" audio assets."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:270 ea588057db2b4248ac74242d5f13e098
msgid "Upmix"
msgstr "Upmix"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:272 b24f32bfd22c43329bfc1e226ad33e10
msgid "Upmix 即上混，是把较少的输入声道分配到更多输出声道。例如把单声道音效送到立体声输出， 或者把立体声音乐送到 5.1 输出。"
msgstr ""
"Upmix means distributing fewer input channels to more output channels. "
"For example, sending a mono sound effect to stereo output, or sending "
"stereo music to 5.1 output."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:275 ebad2d61381e4b6dbc487f82cf1cd0ff
msgid "最常见的单声道到立体声上混，是把同一份单声道信号同时送到左右声道。听感上它会位于正中间。 如果希望这个单声道声音偏左，可以降低右声道电平："
msgstr ""
"The most common mono-to-stereo upmix sends the same mono signal to both "
"left and right channels, which sounds centered. If you want the mono "
"sound to lean left, reduce the right channel level:"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:278 1e97b52ea25446f88fc61d4602ddac05
msgid "单声道上混到偏左立体声输出的混音矩阵"
msgstr "Mix matrix for upmixing mono to left-biased stereo output"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:283 5e4053b93bf2456083636cfbc35cc1b6
msgid "对应代码可以写成："
msgstr "The corresponding code can be written as:"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:285 788b086801a34db1a30d23b711234bcd
msgid ""
"func mono_to_left_biased_stereo(channel: FmodChannel) -> void:\n"
"    var matrix := PackedFloat32Array([\n"
"        1.0,  # Out L = Mono * 1.0\n"
"        0.35, # Out R = Mono * 0.35\n"
"    ])\n"
"\n"
"    channel.set_mix_matrix(matrix, 2, 1)"
msgstr ""
"func mono_to_left_biased_stereo(channel: FmodChannel) -> void:\n"
"    var matrix := PackedFloat32Array([\n"
"        1.0,  # Out L = Mono * 1.0\n"
"        0.35, # Out R = Mono * 0.35\n"
"    ])\n"
"\n"
"    channel.set_mix_matrix(matrix, 2, 1)"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:295 912f8534f25e463dbc84a4bc6ff438f7
msgid ""
"在 Godot-FmodPlayer 中，简单左右声像通常直接用 :ref:`FmodChannelControl.set_pan"
"()<FmodChannelControl-set_pan>` 更方便。 只有在需要精确控制多声道分配时，才需要手动设置混音矩阵。"
msgstr ""
"In Godot-FmodPlayer, simple left/right panning is usually easier with "
":ref:`FmodChannelControl.set_pan()<FmodChannelControl-set_pan>`. Manually"
" set the mix matrix only when precise multi-channel distribution is "
"needed."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:302 03e7c6a129844888a4013be6e9375e2f
msgid "Downmix"
msgstr "Downmix"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:304 6f83f6d6fe4349648b9691ed907ce389
msgid "Downmix 即下混，是把较多的输入声道折叠到较少输出声道。例如把立体声转为单声道， 或者把 5.1 输出到立体声设备。"
msgstr ""
"Downmix means folding more input channels into fewer output channels. For"
" example, converting stereo to mono, or outputting 5.1 content to a "
"stereo device."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:307 16c445255d5646b587c4d13b0b9b96ef
msgid "一个常见的立体声到单声道下混矩阵如下："
msgstr "A common stereo-to-mono downmix matrix is:"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:309 27f850bf44884d9d8a831e44ca22beda
msgid "立体声下混到单声道的混音矩阵"
msgstr "Mix matrix for downmixing stereo to mono"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:314 007b08dad01e4fa1adfdd41a97ecb7a5
msgid "这表示左右声道各取一半相加："
msgstr "This means the left and right channels are each added at half level:"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:316 f24886f0728345c9b6bf7b479257b215
msgid "输出 Mono = 输入 L * 0.5 + 输入 R * 0.5"
msgstr "Output Mono = Input L * 0.5 + Input R * 0.5"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:320 a7b10784c02045aaa22a5a5418337792
msgid ""
"不要简单使用 ``1.0 + 1.0`` 做下混。两个满电平信号直接相加可能让输出超过正常范围， 造成削波或听感上的突然变大。实际项目里可以从 "
"``0.5``、``0.707`` 或更保守的值开始， 再根据素材响度和目标平台调整。"
msgstr ""
"Do not simply use ``1.0 + 1.0`` for downmixing. Adding two full-level "
"signals directly can exceed the normal range, causing clipping or a "
"sudden loudness increase. In real projects, start with ``0.5``, "
"``0.707``, or a more conservative value, then adjust based on material "
"loudness and the target platform."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:324 835bc58248544f1ab5d8875f484477a4
msgid "代码示例："
msgstr "Code example:"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:326 e241b56142b5449ba8221354c015c83b
msgid ""
"func stereo_to_mono(channel: FmodChannel) -> void:\n"
"    var matrix := PackedFloat32Array([\n"
"        0.5, 0.5, # Out Mono = In L * 0.5 + In R * 0.5\n"
"    ])\n"
"\n"
"    channel.set_mix_matrix(matrix, 1, 2)"
msgstr ""
"func stereo_to_mono(channel: FmodChannel) -> void:\n"
"    var matrix := PackedFloat32Array([\n"
"        0.5, 0.5, # Out Mono = In L * 0.5 + In R * 0.5\n"
"    ])\n"
"\n"
"    channel.set_mix_matrix(matrix, 1, 2)"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:336 d4458d9a00344465989b82da1884cd03
msgid "5.1 到立体声的简化示例"
msgstr "Simplified 5.1-to-stereo example"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:338 e0fe0b9ad52b4bb787da99368c985008
msgid "5.1 声道通常可以按以下顺序理解："
msgstr "5.1 channels can usually be understood in this order:"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:340 069c1b8c1de1457bbc2b3b99314c96c8
msgid "Front Left, Front Right, Center, LFE, Surround Left, Surround Right"
msgstr "Front Left, Front Right, Center, LFE, Surround Left, Surround Right"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:344 f8ce234b7e9a4c1e823d700c161e0eef
msgid "一个简化的 5.1 到立体声下混矩阵可以写成："
msgstr "A simplified 5.1-to-stereo downmix matrix can be written as:"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:346 1658f75f6d014587be9f40b1d370ff05
msgid "5.1 声道下混到立体声的混音矩阵"
msgstr "Mix matrix for downmixing 5.1 channels to stereo"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:351 340c0d80bf584dd0b129195f5d859ff9
msgid "这里的思路是："
msgstr "The idea is:"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:353 73b75b11da634f96a31d7defc6d3298c
msgid "左前和右前分别进入对应的左右输出。"
msgstr "Front left and front right go to the corresponding left and right outputs."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:354 9da2cc109ef1444aae49753b55ee2348
msgid "中置声道同时进入左右输出，并降低到 ``0.707``，避免居中内容过响。"
msgstr ""
"The center channel goes to both left and right output, reduced to "
"``0.707`` to avoid making centered content too loud."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:355 15bb9b0afd8d414f8a28e8837534d581
msgid "左环绕进入左输出，右环绕进入右输出，也适当降低。"
msgstr ""
"Surround left goes to left output, and surround right goes to right "
"output, also reduced appropriately."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:356 ad922eeafb5f4902ac7ed3dc9ea6aaf2
msgid "LFE 是低频效果声道，不一定适合直接混入普通立体声输出，是否加入要看项目需求。"
msgstr ""
"LFE is the low-frequency effects channel and may not be suitable for "
"direct mixing into regular stereo output; whether to include it depends "
"on the project."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:360 abece1b1bb354caeaec03aeceb9aec87
msgid "多声道下混没有唯一正确答案。不同平台、设备、耳机虚拟环绕、影院标准和游戏风格可能需要不同矩阵。 对关键内容做下混时，必须用实际目标设备听测。"
msgstr ""
"There is no single correct answer for multi-channel downmixing. Different"
" platforms, devices, virtual surround headphones, cinema standards, and "
"game styles may require different matrices. For critical content, always "
"listen on the actual target device."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:366 d697b01b45d54dcf8b078570026d146e
msgid "Callback"
msgstr "Callback"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:368 d90ad980b430479cb95ca8250cd92793
msgid "Callback 即回调。FMOD 会在特定事件发生时通知用户代码，例如声音结束、通道状态变化或某些底层系统事件。"
msgstr ""
"Callback means FMOD notifies user code when a specific event occurs, such"
" as a sound ending, a channel state change, or a lower-level system "
"event."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:370 46bbf1ccc7f04457aa99faa2f8faf4ba
msgid ""
"在 Godot-FmodPlayer 中，ChannelControl 级别回调会通过 ``callback_received`` 信号转发到 "
"Godot。 每个 System、ChannelControl 或 DSP 通常只维护一个回调入口，因此注册回调时应根据回调类型区分处理逻辑。"
msgstr ""
"In Godot-FmodPlayer, ChannelControl-level callbacks are forwarded to "
"Godot through the ``callback_received`` signal. Each System, "
"ChannelControl, or DSP usually maintains one callback entry, so callback "
"registration should branch by callback type."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:376 b4ab9253addd4bf6924fc573cd676e03
msgid "System"
msgstr "System"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:378 e732126c15ae4376b0fd90963250d56d
msgid ""
"System 是 FMOD Core API 的核心对象，负责初始化音频设备、创建 Sound、播放声音、管理 Channel、更新混音系统、 "
"获取性能数据和处理录音等底层功能。"
msgstr ""
"System is the core object of the FMOD Core API. It initializes audio "
"devices, creates Sounds, plays sounds, manages Channels, updates the "
"mixing system, retrieves performance data, and handles recording."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:381 6464d8693bb24eaaba618b7a956b176d
msgid ""
"在 Godot-FmodPlayer 中，通常不需要手动创建 System。插件会通过 :ref:`FmodServer<FmodServer>`"
" 初始化并维护主系统。 高级用法可以从 :ref:`FmodServer.get_main_system()<FmodServer-"
"get_main_system>` 获取 :ref:`FmodSystem<FmodSystem>`。"
msgstr ""
"In Godot-FmodPlayer, you usually do not create System manually. The "
"plugin initializes and maintains the main system through "
":ref:`FmodServer<FmodServer>`. Advanced usage can start from "
":ref:`FmodServer.get_main_system()<FmodServer-get_main_system>` and "
":ref:`FmodSystem<FmodSystem>`."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:387 f888c93ad506429cbd6c5825981b9958
msgid "Bank 与 Event"
msgstr "Bank and Event"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:389 97ed37a701114a89aac669878687aac7
msgid ""
"Bank 和 Event 常见于 FMOD 的 Studio 工作流。Godot-FmodPlayer 主要面向 **FMOD Core "
"API**， 重点是音频文件播放、通道控制、DSP 效果、混音总线、3D 音频和性能监控。"
msgstr ""
"Bank and Event are common in the FMOD Studio workflow. Godot-FmodPlayer "
"mainly targets the **FMOD Core API**, focusing on audio file playback, "
"channel control, DSP effects, mixing buses, 3D audio, and performance "
"monitoring."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:392 db31c219e5ac40e8a75172a25fb769a3
msgid ""
"因此，在本插件文档中看到 ``Bank`` 或 ``Event`` 时，通常只是为了帮助理解 FMOD 生态中的相关概念。 如果项目需要完整的 "
"FMOD Studio Event、Bank 构建、参数自动化和音频设计师工作流， 应选择专门的 FMOD Studio 集成方案，而不是把 "
"Godot-FmodPlayer 当作完整 Studio 集成使用。"
msgstr ""
"Therefore, when ``Bank`` or ``Event`` appears in this plugin "
"documentation, it is usually only to help explain related FMOD ecosystem "
"concepts. If a project needs a full FMOD Studio Event workflow, Bank "
"builds, parameter automation, and audio-designer tooling, choose a "
"dedicated FMOD Studio integration instead of treating Godot-FmodPlayer as"
" one."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:399 87a50c04b0e24a5cb995e1f837a2fdb5
msgid "FSB"
msgstr "FSB"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:401 f8dc4d67f8f8447db86aa18dad96f338
msgid "FSB 是 FMOD Sample Bank 的缩写，是一种打包采样数据的格式。它和 Studio 工作流中的 Bank 不是同一个概念。"
msgstr ""
"FSB stands for FMOD Sample Bank. It is a format for packed sample data "
"and is not the same concept as a Bank in the Studio workflow."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:403 10c2d89c88604e2b96298fd92420ef18
msgid ""
"Godot-FmodPlayer 面向常规音频文件和 FMOD Core API 用法时，通常不需要直接处理 FSB。 "
"如果项目依赖特殊打包格式，应先确认当前目标平台、FMOD Engine 版本和插件导入流程是否支持。"
msgstr ""
"For regular audio files and FMOD Core API usage, Godot-FmodPlayer usually"
" does not require direct FSB handling. If your project depends on a "
"special packaged format, first confirm support for the target platform, "
"FMOD Engine version, and plugin import flow."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:409 6f2604829e5f4cdbaa8af22122d19edf
msgid "Profiler"
msgstr "Profiler"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:411 a1757129ef5b47fdad320868bcad2013
msgid "Profiler 是用于观察音频系统运行状态的工具。它可以帮助定位 CPU 占用、流式读取、通道数量、DSP 开销和混音问题。"
msgstr ""
"A Profiler is a tool for observing the runtime state of the audio system."
" It helps locate CPU usage, streaming reads, channel count, DSP cost, and"
" mixing issues."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:413 f3c6bd94ce134ac19c42ba94bb6ad6ce
msgid ""
"Godot-FmodPlayer 会把部分 FMOD 性能数据注册到 Godot 的性能监视器中，例如 ``FmodCPUUsage/DSP``、"
" ``FmodCPUUsage/Stream`` 和 "
"``FmodFileUsage/StreamBytesRead``。调试卡顿、爆音或加载异常时，建议同时查看 Godot 输出面板和性能监视器。"
msgstr ""
"Godot-FmodPlayer registers some FMOD performance data in Godot's "
"performance monitors, such as ``FmodCPUUsage/DSP``, "
"``FmodCPUUsage/Stream``, and ``FmodFileUsage/StreamBytesRead``. When "
"debugging stutters, pops, or loading issues, check these monitors first."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:419 dd3c545969f343878be4d6e9c0cab5c6
msgid "运行库"
msgstr "Runtime Library"

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:421 eee9188a6faf4bbd98d17597d523b18f
msgid ""
"运行库指 FMOD Engine 在目标平台上的二进制文件，例如 Windows 上的 ``fmod.dll``，Android 上的 "
"``libfmod.so`` 和相关 Java 文件。"
msgstr ""
"A runtime library is the FMOD Engine binary for the target platform, such"
" as ``fmod.dll`` on Windows or ``libfmod.so`` and related Java files on "
"Android."

#: ../../source/glossary.rst:423 4da975b77d7b434ca6f963d1a1da8958
msgid ""
"Godot-FmodPlayer 插件本身不分发 FMOD 运行库。你需要根据目标平台从 FMOD 官方渠道获取，并按 :doc:`export`"
" 或 :doc:`getting_started/installation` 的说明放到项目中。发布游戏时还需要遵守 FMOD 的许可和署名要求。"
msgstr ""
"Godot-FmodPlayer does not distribute FMOD runtime libraries. Get them "
"from official FMOD channels for your target platform and place them in "
"the project as described in :doc:`export` or "
":doc:`getting_started/installation`. When publishing a game, you must "
"also follow FMOD licensing and attribution requirements."

